Steps:
   1. Install RLGlue:
      http://glue.rl-community.org

   2. Set $JAVA_HOME properly:
      export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java 

   3. make


Also see:
   * http://2009.rl-competition.org/
   * http://2009.rl-competition.org/tetris.php
   * Q-Learning By Examples:  http://people.revoledu.com/kardi/tutorial/ReinforcementLearning/index.html

